<item>
            <title>[LU-11881] lctl pool_list: Value too large for defined data type (75)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11881</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;he &quot;lctl pool_list&quot; command displays an error message but returns the correct data and exits with a zero return status. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;[admin@snx11281n002 ~]$ lctl pool_list snx11281
Pools from snx11281:
lctl pool_list: Error reading pool list for &apos;snx11281&apos;: Value too large for defined data type (75)
Pools from snx11281:
snx11281.fs
snx11281.oss0
snx11281.oss1
snx11281.oss2
snx11281.oss3
snx11281.ssu0
snx11281.ssu1
[admin@snx11281n002 ~]$ echo $?
0
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
